OverallGame

Class gameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • OverallGame.gameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Animal, Beached, Boat, G4Player, Player, Scoreboard, Trash

    public class gameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    gameObject is a class used as a mold for all of the gameObjects in each game. A gameObject has a position, velocity, and a name.
    Version:
    5/17
    Author:
    Team 7
